{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "24.1",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b80a1cea",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……もうダメ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e98dc9cb",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "おつかれ、様……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "85de398a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "チラシズシを食べるコハルが箸を置く。……皿には米粒ひとつ残っておらず、思わず感心した。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "18a93fc9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハルもギブアップか。これでコハルは３位だな。村じゃそう思ったこと無いけど、結構食べられるんだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.1",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5277c9a2",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "まだ全然入るけど、これ以上は勿体ないわよ！　美味しいって感じる間だけ食べないと！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9b8cae",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そうか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.1",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "78335335",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "これで残ったのは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.1",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5b03b033",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "は！　そろそろギブアップしたらどうだい、お姫様！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.1",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fef0ce1",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "だ～れが！　そっちこそスピードが落ちておるぞ、さっさと降参せい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.1",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "189535cd",
      "speaker": "マロウ",
      "ja": "おやびーん！　がんばれーっ！　一週間分くらい食べ貯めるっすー！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.1",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9a275973",
      "speaker": "モル",
      "ja": "………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "93c8ffba",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "トーリとアイディルか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.1",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "228f8416",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "２人とも、すごい……みんなで暴飲暴食……お祭りらしいね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6920afbf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そうか……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.1",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "95d5a9e1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ですが、これは長引くでしょうね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.1",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5042dc32",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうね、２人とも負けず嫌いっぽいし……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.1",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "370a3317",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いいえ、そうではありません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.1",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "11e0cf59",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "えっ？　違うの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.1",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5e156d4a",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "リリアンは、魔力としてカロリーをある程度放出することができます。大食い中でもそれは可能……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.1",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4a6fa902",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "恐らく無意識ですが、２人ともその戦法を使っているようです。限度は勿論ありますが、限界はかなり遠いかと",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "79694d5e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "へえ……な、なるほど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.1",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "996124bf",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あなたがぶっちぎりで最下位だったのもその関係です。ご安心ください",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "839f0172",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そりゃどうも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.1",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "430ebbd1",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "ごくごくごく……っ、ぷはーっ！　甘酒、おかわり！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.1",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "667b099a",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "……くっは～！　こっちもじゃ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5ae6332c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "流石にお酒は危ないんじゃあ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.1",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "186e57b4",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "リリアンならアルコールの分解も早いから大丈夫よ？　普通に飲めば酔うけど、本気になれば水みたいなもんよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "745a29cc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "マジで……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.1",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "14f7f1a7",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "まあ、個人差はあるでしょうけど……あたしはお酒飲んだら割と普通に酔っちゃうし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.1",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7aa05539",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "やれやれ……流石にこれ以上時間はかけられません。こうしましょう",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.1",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6d10f8e6",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ここからは、こちらのみお食べください",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.1",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "449162b6",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "なっ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.1",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "59c5d863",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "これは……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "705cc3bb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "トーリ、アイディルの前に並べられ、積み重ねられる色鮮やかな四角い物体。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.1",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ffa4627e",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "菱餅……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.1",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "34e095c",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こちらであれば、リリアンと言えど長続きはしないでしょう。ラストスパートですよお二方",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "176.1",
      "line_index": 176,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "125531e6",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "くっ……やってやる！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.1",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "180ce958",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "負けるか……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.1",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "17cfd9",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "ふ……あ、甘い物は別腹と言うが、流石に餅は辛いのう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.1",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "af0d11a",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "最初は美味しかったけど、今はもう……アゴが疲れて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.1",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d3cefaac",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "ふ……ふん、わらわは普段からこの食事で鍛えられておるわい！　まだまだいけるわ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.1",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8b2f3148",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "こ、こんなところで、アイディル海賊団の船長が……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "203.1",
      "line_index": 203,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c422404d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "負けてたまるかってのよーっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.0",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a3f1f5b0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うおっ、凄い勢いだ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "207.1",
      "line_index": 207,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5f0d5d05",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "くっ、抜かされてしま……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "214.1",
      "line_index": 214,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "32cfd533",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "っ………………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "221.1",
      "line_index": 221,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b43fd131",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "～～～～～っ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.1",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ca5526bc",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "の、喉に詰まらせたのか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.0",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "88465f46",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "み、水を……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.1",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bc1c3be8",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "げほっ、げほっ……！　あー、死ぬかと思った！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "246.1",
      "line_index": 246,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3b196693",
      "speaker": "モル",
      "ja": "……すみません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.1",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ec4a07de",
      "speaker": "モル",
      "ja": "祭っていうのは……節度を持って……楽しむ物だと思います……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.1",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a20981d0",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "は、はいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "253.1",
      "line_index": 253,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "de929d5c",
      "speaker": "トーリ",
      "ja": "い、言う通りじゃな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "255.0",
      "line_index": 255,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c3d87119",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（モルも怒ったりするんだな……）",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
